        "name": "Know thy Doom",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "As your legend grows, details of your demise become clearer. And you know that it is not yet your time. You can attempt a recovery check using your dying value before it increases, rolling twice and taking the better result. Regardless of the outcome, reduce your doomed value by 1.",
